      "para_id": "Q000999.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Šara , the confidant of An , the beloved child of Inana , his father , Šu-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , built the E-šage-pada , his beloved temple for his ( own ) well-being ."
    }
  ],
